        "description": {
            "value": "<p>You refract latent energy from the Dimension of Time into your current plane in the form of a massive blade. The blade deals 5d6 slashing damage to all creatures in the area as it causes time to pass rapidly in a thin slice of their bodies. Creatures in the area must attempt a Fortitude save.</p><hr /><p><strong>Critical Success</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p>\n<p><strong>Success</strong> The creature takes half damage.</p>\n<p><strong>Failure</strong> The creature takes full damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 1}.</p>\n<p><strong>Critical Failure</strong> The creature takes double damage and is @UUID[Compendium.sf2e.conditions.Item.Sickened]{Sickened 2}.</p><hr /><p><strong>Heightened (+1)</strong> The damage increases by 2d6.</p>"
